  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of civil society organizations to promote human rights in Mongolian prisons</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Rozvoj organiz&#xE1;ci&#xED; ob&#x10D;ianskej spolo&#x10D;nosti s cie&#x13E;om podpory dodr&#x17E;iavania &#x13E;udsk&#xFD;ch pr&#xE1;v v mongolsk&#xFD;ch v&#xE4;zniciach</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;k sa bude v spolupr&#xE1;ci s pracovn&#xED;kmi Charitas &#x10C;esk&#xE1; republika venova&#x165; nasledovn&#xFD;m &#x10D;innostiam: - Spolupr&#xE1;ca na pr&#xED;prave tr&#xE9;ningov&#xFD;ch modulov pre mongolsk&#xFD;ch soci&#xE1;lnych pracovn&#xED;kov - Pomoc pri v&#xFD;skume dodr&#x17E;iavania &#x13E;udsk&#xFD;ch pr&#xE1;v vo v&#xE4;zniciach v Mongolsku - Budovanie vlastn&#xFD;ch kapac&#xED;t pre bud&#xFA;ce projekty v Mongolsku - Rozv&#xED;janie spolupr&#xE1;ce &#x10C;VO a Charitas &#x10C;esk&#xE1; republika - Identifik&#xE1;cia mo&#x17E;nost&#xED; odborn&#xE9;ho zapojenia slovensk&#xFD;ch subjektov do projektov v oblasti good governance v Mongolsku - Budovanie kapac&#xED;t &#x10C;VO v oblasti monitoringu dodr&#x17E;iavania &#x13E;udsk&#xFD;ch pr&#xE1;v a vzdel&#xE1;vania v oblasti &#x13E;udsk&#xFD;ch pr&#xE1;v vo v&#xE4;zniciach, - V r&#xE1;mci pon&#xE1;vratov&#xFD;ch aktiv&#xED;t odovzdanie sk&#xFA;senost&#xED; spolupracovn&#xED;kom &#x10C;VO ako aj in&#xFD;m slovensk&#xFD;m MVRO, ktor&#xE9; prejavia z&#xE1;ujem &#x2013; formou workshopu.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Volunteer in cooperation with the staff of Caritas Czech Republic will engage in the following activities: - Cooperation in the preparation of training modules for the Mongolian Social Workers - Helping to research human rights in prisons in Mongolia - Building their own capacity for future projects in Mongolia - Developing cooperation Statues - Identification of possible involvement of Slovak entities in projects in the field of good governance in Mongolia - Capacity Building in monitoring of human rights education and human rights in prisons, - Development education activities</narrative>
  </description>
